{"tid":1970352,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩嘅嘢，都係分注好","createTime":"2020-04-13T05:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T10:54:36.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5519e08dc87a7a3163fbcc5b8faa305f24ad8de4","tid":1970352,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"一爆支那肺炎嗰時，口罩期貨升到三萬二，個個都話上三萬六，個個驚死入唔到貨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都要用嘅，我都貴價買咗 1 盒。不過其實爆升之前都一早入咗 5 盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到而家啲做傳統業務嘅廢港商家又冷醒，個個都衝去生產品罩，支那嗰邊又復工，啲口罩期貨跌到二萬一，個個又話下望萬六，真係笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排外國疫情又話緊張，啲口罩期貨又升到二萬四，啲人又搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都話咗買賣嘅嘢，分注做㗎啦，如果唔係又高揸低沽㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5721131aa168764d7467ede16a59e497e3467172","tid":1970352,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"IT9 evolve左（個名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa42a1258868bfbc010bcbb75e1e351c57956dde","tid":1970352,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5721131aa168764d7467ede16a59e497e3467172","tid":1970352,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"IT9 evolve左（個名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"冇變，都係窮三代，只不過揼垃圾同時做埋基金經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9536ac87dd0d9f135bf85f85613c80da0db35d51","tid":1970352,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"一早二月頭熊撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cae0de8a2c7b6703eb7918f7287ff038c39cd52","tid":1970352,"uid":130742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"仲懶醒，大把醒目連登仔1，2月頭all in真「正」價口罩全部疫前價位入日美貨，洗鬼跟你平均成本法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873d0b25a8e4bc74c3e1664e68fecbc6b83d2391","tid":1970352,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"我係上年低位細注入貨  作後備<br />\n結果比D三姑六婆恥笑黑色口罩冇人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到自己啲貨升左三倍  個個爭住買<br />\n到我笑番佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：因為要自用所以唔平倉"}]}